{"tid":637861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墳場下爭山水　兩晨運客打交","createTime":"2018-04-22T08:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T09:10:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9bfc8220cbafb1bebd32a7384a160badcfa115","tid":637861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369095?_ga=2.112240388.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369095%3F_ga%3D2.112240388.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=aQe3t%2B%2BtQzHLQ0HOokJk7b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f36253dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180422%2F20369095%3F_ga%3D2.112240388.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=314e0590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180422/20369095?_ga=2.112240388.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n墳場下爭山水　兩晨運客打交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180422/large/22la6p07new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180422%2Flarge%2F22la6p07new.jpg&h=09874835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■事發後，附近居民陳伯如常帶備兩個水樽取水。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩名男子昨晨於將軍澳一處山坡取山水時，疑因先後次序問題爭執，最終大打出手，兩敗俱傷，警方接報到場將兩人送院，其後兩人同涉嫌普通襲擊罪被捕。<br />\n將軍澳澳景路全長約2.3公里，首尾兩端連接藍田碧雲道及維景灣畔，山坡上方為將軍澳華人永遠墳場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳有益　有人引喉取10瓶<br />\n<br />\n西貢區議員陳繼偉表示，每日都有一批晨運客固定到山坡取山水，他們聲稱山水水質甘甜，有益健康，惟山坡貼近墳場，恐水質受污染，區內居民較少取水，以外來人佔大多數。昨晨10時許，兩名分別73歲姓李及53歲姓黃的男子，各自帶備水樽器皿到山坡取山水，其間就排隊問題發生衝突，並大打出手，有人持枴杖襲擊對方，同時亦被對方推跌，最終兩敗俱傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場將兩人送院敷治，其後以普通襲擊拘捕兩人。將軍澳居民陳伯昨亦帶備兩個礦泉水樽到來取山水，他指每日均有很多人來取山水，部份更駕車來引膠喉落山盛10個水瓶帶走。陳伯指這處的山水水質佳，但他強調自己會煲滾後才用來煮食或飲用，多年來相安無事，不擔心會有衞生問題。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n圍毆餐廳東主　兩男長洲落網<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n「奇怪動物」紅頰獴鬧市亂跑"},{"pid":"72ee73b18c46247d4ea086be817823bf15a9379c","tid":637861,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"咁大樽水行山，仲要兩樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da2f7f53877eac813b726fa2ca8f258b8150b18","tid":637861,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ee73b18c46247d4ea086be817823bf15a9379c","tid":637861,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"咁大樽水行山，仲要兩樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:10:16.000Z","msg":"佢地有手推車"}]}